<head>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag params[:controller] %>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="columns has-text-centered">
    <div class="column">
    </div>
    <div class="column is-three-quarters-mobile is-one-half-desktop">
    <%= image_tag("dark_logo_transparent.svg", :alt => "rss feed") %>
  </div>
  <div class="column">
  </div>
  </div>
      <section class="section">
      <div class = "container has-text-centered">
          <span>When we dream at night, we enter <a href=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rapid_eye_movement_sleep>REM Sleep</a>. In this stage, we process dreams,
            make associations and form memories. REM sleep is considered biologically necessary
            for all birds and mammals and even occurs in fetuses before they can see.</span> <br/><br/>
          <span>During REM sleep, our eyes move rapidly back and forth as we dream vividly.
            In Guided Daydreaming, we mimic this action to help enhance daydreaming. </span>
            <hr>
      </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
          <div class="container">
            <h4 class="title"><strong>Instructions:</strong></h4>
            <h5 class="subtitle">
              During a session, a ball will move back and forth rapidly across your screen.
            </h5>
            <h5 class="subtitle">
              Follow the ball with your eyes and let your mind wander; daydream and jump between ideas, thoughts and memories.
            </h5>
            <h5 class="subtitle">
              When the ball stops, notice where your mind has wandered and let the question that appears guide you down a different path. Explore the new path when the ball starts again.
            </h5>
            <h5 class="subtitle">
            You will find you feel better after a session and have made unexpected associations!
            </h5>
          </div>
    </section>

      <div class = has-text-centered>
          <%= link_to 'Begin', session_path(), class:"button is-primary is-medium" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <br/>


  <footer class="footer intro">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content has-text-right">
        <p>
          <a id="sourceCode" href="https://github.com/marwaybs/guidedDaydreaming">Source Code</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>
  <%= javascript_include_tag params[:controller] %>
</body>
